headline: Raychem RPG: Nearly Four Decades of Engineering Excellence in India's Energy Infrastructure Development
summary: As commuters traverse metro networks across India, as aircraft operations continue at major airports nationwide, and as clean energy is transmitted from Solar Park- the intricate network of precision-engineered electrical connections that enable these modern infrastructure systems remain largely invisible to the public eye.
